name: Nothing to Live For. Nothing to Lose.
description: The thing I'm most horrified of is losing control. Drugs make me feel like I'm losing control of myself, but what do I do when I use drugs when my life gets out of control? When the drugs no longer numb the pain and I'm left alone with a brain that doesn't function right? I'm horrified of death, but I don't know how to live. I don't know which one scares me more.
